{"data":[{"id":563830178,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"a3d60d9a56d06c4d8f4a3df7dae71374","url_token":"hepingjituan","name":"和平集团","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-bdaf98bdf49f56b5832e953e9ffde5b5_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-bdaf98bdf49f56b5832e953e9ffde5b5_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/a3d60d9a56d06c4d8f4a3df7dae71374","user_type":"people","headline":"高中毕业，自诩理性客观但不一定中立的自由意志主义者。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":895,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563830178","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546288865,"updated_time":1546288865,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"comment_count":3,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e我很惊奇地看到，高票答案居然都没有准确找出该证明的错误。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e也许是我哪里搞错了？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个证明的一处错误，在于“如果把-1归到质数的集合中”。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这只是一个描述错误，并非逻辑错误。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e正确的表达是：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e定义“智数”：由-1与全体质数构成的集合。\u003c/b\u003e记为\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=P%5E%7B%2B%7D\" alt=\"P^{+}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e规定A为“全体能表示为两个智数之和的偶数构成的集合”。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e讨论命题X： \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%E8%8B%A5-1%5Cin+P%5E%7B%2B%7D%2C%E5%88%99%5Cforall+n%5Cin+N%5E%7B%2B%7D%2C2n%5Cin+A\" alt=\"若-1\\in P^{+},则\\forall n\\in N^{+},2n\\in A\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其逆否命题X'为: \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%E8%8B%A5%5Cexists+n_%7B0%7D%5Cin+N%5E%7B%2B%7D%2C2n_%7B0%7D%5Cnotin+A%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%99-1%5Cnotin+P%5E%7B%2B%7D\" alt=\"若\\exists n_{0}\\in N^{+},2n_{0}\\notin A，则-1\\notin P^{+}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e∵取\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=n_%7B0%7D%3D1\" alt=\"n_{0}=1\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ，有 \u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=2n_%7B0%7D%3D2%5Cin+A\" alt=\"2n_{0}=2\\in A\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e ，∴X'的前件为假，X'为真命题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e此处是第一处逻辑错误。作者混淆了特称命题与全称命题，误认为举出一个反例即可证明X'的前件为假。但X'的前件是一个存在性命题，是不能用反例来证的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e找到了一处逻辑错误，后面的证明也就没有看的必要了。作者并没有在“若前件为假，则命题为真”这一逻辑基础上犯错。\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e毫无疑问，这个证明的作者水准不足，犯了很低级的错误。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但我想，如果他没有故意哗众取宠的话，这也不能构成大家肆意嘲讽他的理由吧？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我看他的态度，像是在承认错误的样子。咱们没必要太得理不饶人。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"我很惊奇地看到，高票答案居然都没有准确找出该证明的错误。也许是我哪里搞错了？ 这个证明的一处错误，在于“如果把-1归到质数的集合中”。这只是一个描述错误，并非逻辑错误。正确的表达是： \u003cb\u003e定义“智数”：由-1与全体质数构成的集合。\u003c/b\u003e记为P^{+}。规定A为…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Cco